00:00:02.860 --> 00:00:05.020
Hello and welcome to today's lecture.

00:00:05.720 --> 00:00:09.280
The personality that we're going to talk about is called The Tank.

00:00:09.280 --> 00:00:10.320
Who is the Tank?

00:00:10.960 --> 00:00:14.020
This person tends to be overconfident.

00:00:14.320 --> 00:00:19.840
When his aims are put in jeopardy, he takes out all his anger on the person in front of him. 

00:00:20.140 --> 00:00:27.480
He has nothing personal against him, but there are 2 main purposes behind taking out his angry. 

00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:30.800
The first one is that he wants something to be done in perfect time.

00:00:31.040 --> 00:00:32.760
The second one is that he wants it done in the best way.

00:00:33.180 --> 00:00:36.640
So, who is this person? We'll understand more through this video.

00:00:38.580 --> 00:00:39.080
Hello.

00:00:42.220 --> 00:00:42.980
How are you doing, man?

00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:45.360
Hey, buddy. I'm fine.

00:00:48.420 --> 00:00:50.320
Man, please don't forget about the phone.

00:00:51.860 --> 00:00:55.760
The phone? Yeah, don’t worry. I got this, man. Actually, I'm going to go get it right now.

00:00:55.945 --> 00:01:00.905
Please do. I'll leave it to you, all right? My work depends on it. I've borrowed my friend's phone to call you.

00:01:01.280 --> 00:01:05.560
Okay, don’t worry. I told you I've got this. In fact, I'm on my way to get it. I'll bet there in five minutes

00:01:06.200 --> 00:01:08.780
All right. Thank you. Bye.

